data.description: Fully remodeled turn key 3 bed/3 bath rambler nestled on nearly 5 acres of pure paradise.  So many upgrades to include: new roof, gutters, exterior siding, all windows and trim, sliding glass door, exterior paint, replaced heat pump, furnace and ducting throughout entire home, new 80 gallon electric water heater, well water filtration system, granite counters in bathrooms, kitchen, and laundry room, new waterproof laminate flooring throughout the entire house. Completely remodeled master bath to include a jetted tub! Septic was also just pumped and risers were added.  This house is truly one of a kind and ready for someone to love it as much as the sellers. Pride of ownership shines through in every room! THIS IS A MUST SEE!
